{"tid":1660232,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"［星期日結論］［逆風而行］遊行有批帶gear，守重慶。冇批開花賀佢老母","createTime":"2019-10-17T11:44:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-17T23:34:14.000Z","uid":303304,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"272da35c4024ba2e932c51867f5a324b1cdce8bd","tid":1660232,"uid":303304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T11:44:01.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>咪撚再叫人唔帶gear</strong></span><br />\n無勇武拖住班狗，你地和理非可以次次都玩得咁開心？帶gear有乜問題？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n結果次撚次都有一大班勇武唔帶gear,然後空裝上前線幫你地頂，你地再平安返屋企嘆冷氣上連登屌勇武<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nbtw,<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">如果我1020返到屋企開兒登再見到屌勇武嘅post,我一定屌哂你地老母</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n仲有，南亞刀手好明顯係分化計，唔該大家唔好再種族歧視。好似大把無腦藍絲同左膠係香港人一樣，大把南亞人一樣係手足，當日勇武會幫手守南亞地盤。<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>臥底請勿衝擊勇武防線，否則後果自負</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wQNH2yr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwQNH2yr.jpg&h=65aa6e8b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n以上內容僅限有不反對通知書。<br />\n如果冇，咁梗係十八區開花啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n星期日開花最好嘅結果係令到<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>星期一壞鐵</strong></span>，所以麻煩打鐵嗰時落力啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n話時話，上次開花我個人對港島十分十滿<br />\n當初十月五日，東區嘅鏟泥車同南區嘅第一粒彈去左邊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n下次爭氣啲啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"662ea8c5d8162dae36644a9cd926301d952623f7","tid":1660232,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T11:44:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/W04Z2Gp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FW04Z2Gp.jpg&h=e79a1d2a&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"910d9f716fd672ad450a688402456ea139205523","tid":1660232,"uid":312125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T11:45:41.000Z","msg":"【行動】西九遊行<span style=\"color: red;\">要大量針對強國人文宣</span>！<br />\n務求<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">輸出革命</span></strong>！附詳盡策略：<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1659090\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1659090</a>"},{"pid":"fb5dfd53656ce048a4244db4cc265b781e0b122c","tid":1660232,"uid":17991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T11:58:25.000Z","msg":"行動post推"},{"pid":"377e6b655a536798cc23ae83cddb25af5911dc5b","tid":1660232,"uid":304267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T23:34:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}